(4, 24, 'TH', 31, 'COOKIN’ NANTA SHOW', 'cookin-nanta-show-royal-seat', '<p>The 1st Asian Show on Broadway, New York now arrived in Bangkok. Cookin&rsquo; NANTA Show is a comic non-verbal show for all ages. It is story about kitchen. The kitchen is thrown into a mess and cooks become wild as chefs chop, beat and stir in an attempt to meet the deadline. Kitchen knives &amp; many kitchen materials are transformed into musical instruments with chefs; they make unexpected amazing sound that will make you laugh with love. Cookin&rsquo; NANTA Show is the first Asian show to open its own theatre in Broadway, New York, USA and had Open Run for 3 years from Sep. 2003 to Sep. 2005. Over 10 million audiences from all over the world enjoyed the show. Finally Jan.2013 Cookin&rsquo; NANTA Show opens Bangkok theatre @ RCA, Played 1,000 times and over 100,000 people visited its Bangkok theatre.</p>', '#48C61D', '<p>Show Time: 8pm (Daily show, close first Monday of the month.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 100, 1, 0, 1, 'THB', 20000, 0, 50000, 0, 0, 0, '2016-10-25 18:34:34', 1609350, '{\"1\":\"Hotel shuttle service from MRT Phetchaburi (exit 1) to  NANTA Theatre\"}', '{\"1\":\"Alcoholic drinks\",\"2\":\"Private transfer\"}', 110000, '- Cancellation less than 72 hours to prior to the show, there will be 100% charge\r\n- any kind of amendment must be done 72 hours to prior to the show.\r\n- No show will be charged 100%.', 48, NULL, '2018-01-05 10:23:57', NULL, 'ChIJ82ENKDJgHTERIEjiXbIAAQE', 1, 'NANTA Theatre, R.C.A Plaza, Bldg. Fl.1, Soi Soonwijai, Pharam 9 Rd., Bangkapi, Huaykwang, Bangkok 10310, Thailand', '+66(0)2-641-4407', 59.333333333333, 4.9444444444444, 12, 0, 'Asia/Bangkok', 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 63, 64, 65, '[]', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.532343247813!2d100.57815811420835!3d13.746739601115902!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30e29e5977155587%3A0xebb209d5e20ab35e!2sNANTA+B