(5, 24, 'TH', 31, 'COOKIN’ NANTA SHOW (Standard Seat)', 'cookin-nanta-show-standard-seat', 'The 1st Asian Show on Broadway, New York now arrived in Bangkok. Cookin’ NANTA Show is a comic non-verbal show for all ages. It is story about kitchen. The kitchen is thrown into a mess and cooks become wild as chefs chop, beat and stir in an attempt to meet the deadline. Kitchen knives & many kitchen materials are transformed into musical instruments with chefs; they make unexpected amazing sound that will make you laugh with love. Cookin’ NANTA Show is the first Asian show to open its own theatre in Broadway, New York, USA and had Open Run for 3 years from Sep. 2003 to Sep. 2005. Over 10 million audiences from all over the world enjoyed the show. Finally Jan.2013 Cookin’ NANTA Show opens Bangkok theatre @ RCA, Played 1,000 times and over 100,000 people visited its Bangkok theatre.', '#B02874', '<p>Show Time: 8pm (Daily show, close first Monday of the month.)</p><p><strong>Tour Location :</strong> NANTA Theatre, R.C.A Plaza, Bldg. Fl.1, Soi Soonwijai, Pharam 9 Rd., Bangkapi, Huaykwang, Bangkok 10310, Thailand</p><p><strong>Emergency Call</strong></p><p>+66(0)2-641-4407</p>', 100, 1, 0, 1, 'THB', 23000, 0, 50000, 0, 0, 0, '2016-10-25 18:52:51', 1609350, '{\"1\":\"Hotel shuttle service from MRT Phetchaburi (exit 1) to  NANTA Theatre\"}', '[]', 110000, '- Cancellation less than 24 hours to prior to the show, there will be 100% charge\r\n- any kind of amendment must be done 48 hours to prior to the show.\r\n- No show will be charged 100%.', 48, NULL, '2016-11-04 12:55:24', '2017-02-07 12:34:49', 'ChIJsU1CR_eNTTARAuhXB4gs154', 1, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Asia/Bangkok', 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 63, 64, 65, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(6, 25, 'TH', 31, 'Art in Paradise Chiang Mai', 'art-in-paradise-chiang-mai', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">Art in Paradise (Chiang Mai) the first Illusion Art Museum of Chiangmai, presents Illusion Art, the painting art requiring techniques and expertise in painting on a flat surface into a &quot;3D&quot; and giving a sense of realistic art. In addition, the museum also offers artworks in the form that allow visitors to take part in the artworks closely (Interactive Art), where the visitors can take photos with creative imagination, emotion and postures designed to correspond with each painting according to their own preferences as if they are a part of the painting. Therefore, Art in Paradise (Chiang Mai) is where the art is understandable for everyone, and happiness and entertainment are delivered to the visitor as well.</span></p>', '#064005', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><strong>Opening Time:</strong><br />\r\n9am - 9pm. &nbsp;(Open daily)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 300, 1, 1, 1, 'THB', 18000, 0, 12000, 0, 0, 0, '2016-10-25 22:56:08', 1153671, '[]', '{\"1\":\"Pick up service\",\"2\":\"Food & Beverages\"}', 40000, '- Cancellation less than 72 hours to prior to the activity, there will be 100% charge\r\n- Any kind of amendment must be done 72 hours to prior to the activity.\r\n- No show will be charged 100%.', 39, 0, '2017-12-26 06:30:12', NULL, 'ChIJXW-7kH462jARZ0ObpXBi1Jg', 1, '199/9 Changklan Rd. Changklan, Chiang Mai, Thailand 50200', '+66 (0) 53274100', 10, 5, 2, 0, 'Asia/Bangkok', 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 63, 67, 68, '[\"art in paradise chiang mai\",\"3d art gallery chiangmai\",\"chiangmai art museum\",\"3rd art chiangmai\",\"Illusion art museum\",\"Illusion art chiangmai\",\"chiangmai art in paradise\",\"art in paradise 3d museum\"]', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3777.4934709157865!2d98.99716071427174!3d18.7761