(7, 26, 'TH', 31, 'Paint Bar Bangkok', 'paint-bar-bangkok', '<p>เพ้นบาร์แบงค็อก (Paint Bar Bangkok) อาร์ตบาร์คอนเซ็ปใหม่สุดฮิปแห่งแรกและแห่งเดียวในเอเชีย ที่ซึ่งเหล่าคนดังให้ความนิยมเป็นอย่างมาก เหมาะสำหรับผู้ที่กำลังมองหาสถานที่แฮงค์เอาท์แห่งใหม่ พลาดไม่ได้ที่จะแวะมาจิบเครื่องดื่มชั้นดี ทานของว่างจานอร่อย ตวัดพู่กันตามจังหวะเสียงเพลงในร้านสไตล์ อินดัสเทรียล ลอฟท์ (Industrial Loft) ชมวิวสวยใจกลางเมือง ได้รังสรรค์ผลงานชิ้นเอกที่มีเพียงชิ้นเดียวในโลก และสังสรรค์กับเพื่อน หรือคนรู้ใจไปพร้อมๆ กัน</p>', '#CE3A4E', '<p><strong>วันและเวลาทำการ</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>เปิดทำการทุกวันอังคาร&nbsp;- วันอาทิตย์<strong> (</strong><strong>ยกเว้นวันจันทร์</strong><strong>)*</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>รอบเย็น &nbsp;เริ่ม 14.30 น. - 17.00 น.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รอบค่ำ &nbsp; &nbsp;เริ่ม&nbsp;19.30 น. - 22.00 น.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*หมายเหตุ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- รายการอาหารและเครื่องดื่มไม่รวมอยู่ในแพคเกจ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-วันและเวลาอาจมีการเปลี่ยนแปลงขึ้นอยู่กับเงื่อนไขที่ผู้จัดกำหนด</p>', 20, 1, 0, 1, 'THB', 8000, 0, 68000, 0, 0, 0, '2016-10-26 11:31:15', 1609350, '[]', '{\"1\":\"\\u0e2d\\u0e32\\u0e2b\\u0e32\\u0e23\\u0e41\\u0e25\\u0e30\\u0e40\\u0e04\\u0e23\\u0e37\\u0e48\\u0e2d\\u0e07\\u0e14\\u0e37\\u0e48\\u0e21\"}', 79900, 'ไม่มีการยกเลิก', 44, NULL, '2017-09-26 08:29:21', NULL, 'ChIJ82ENKDJgHTERIEjiXbIAAQE', 1, 'ชั้น 6 โครงการพิมาน 49\r\n46/4 สุขุมวิท ซอย 49 แขวง คลองตัน เขต วัฒนา\r\nกทมฯ 10110', '+66810010849', 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Asia/Bangkok', 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 63, 64, 65, '[]', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.773726887355!2d100.57438471420818!3d13.73214470144991!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30e29faac8bea223%3A0xeeddf5de405d7840!2sPaintbar+Bangkok!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1505889283208\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(8, 27, 'TH', 32, 'ABC Morning Tour', 'abc-morning-tour', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Get out of your bed early at least for one day and get your lazy bones to work- to be precise physical work. And trust me, you&rsquo;ll love what you&rsquo;ll do, I guarantee! Head towards Khlong tan area (ABC Office) and find yourself among cyclists that are there for the same purpose as you: sightseeing the lively streets of <strong><a href=\"https://www.amujamu.com/en/locations/thailand/central-thailand/bangkok\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Bangkok</span></a></strong> by peddling on their cycles. As fun as it sounds, the experience will be so much more refreshing than you could have imagined.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">ABC Morning Tour(<strong><a href=\"https://www.amujamu.com/en/search/tours?q=abc&amp;date_range_start=&amp;date_range_end=&amp;category=&amp;location=&amp;creator_id=&amp;min_price=0&amp;max_price=0&amp;min_rating=&amp;page=\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Amazing Bangkok Cyclist</span></a></strong>) offers you with the opportunity to see and know the city in depth and at different hours. The locals, their morning rituals, how the street vendors set up their shops for breakfast and the morning view of the place, all combined shall be an adventurous morning all the way.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">When you are done crossing the Chao River with the help of our guide, on a long tail boat, you will be at the greener part of Bangkok even before you know. A beautiful and natural side of Bangkok awaits you there filled with green forests and its habitats.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Explore the nature of Bangkok on your two wheels while you make a stop at the oasis for a break to cherish your surroundings.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Highlights:</span></strong></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Sightseeing the lively streets of Bangkok</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Freshly made foods from different vendors</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Amazing Chao Phraya River crossing on long tail boat</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', '#CEB337', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><strong>Tour&nbsp;Duration:</strong>&nbsp;08.00 AM-12.00 PM&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Distance:</strong>&nbsp;Approximately 13-16 km</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\"><strong>Meeting point</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">ABC Office:&nbsp;10/ 5-7, Soi Ari, Sukhumvit Road Soi 26, Klongton, Klong Toey, Bangkok 10110, Thailand.</span></p>', 10, 1, 0, 1, 'THB', 26000, 0, 104000, 0, 0, 0, '2016-10-27 13:21:05', 1609350, '[\"Coffee or tea upon arrival\",\"Free use of the internet\",\"Free photo\\u2019s of the day\",\"Comfortable and well maintained mountain or city bikes\",\"Water , fruit, snacks , soft drink\",\"Guide fee\",\"Boat transfers,\",\"Refreshing towel upon return\"]', '[\"Pick up and drop off from your hotel,\",\"Any extra drinks\\/food not provided by your guide,\",\"Any alcoholic drinks are prohibited during the tours,\",\"Transportation costs if the customer wish to return to before the end of the tour.\"]', 130000, '- Cancellation less than 72 hours to prior to the activity, there will be 100% charge\r\n- Any kind of amendment must be done 48 hours to prior to the activity.\r\n- No show will be charged 100%.', 29, NULL, '2017-10-05 09:40:01', NULL, 'ChIJ82ENKDJgHTERIEjiXbIAAQE', 1, 'ABC Office : 10/ 5-7, Soi Ari, Sukhumvit Road Soi 26, Klongton, Klong Toey, Bangkok 10110, Thailand', '+6626656364', 14.333333333333, 4.7777777777778, 3, 0, 'Asia/Bangkok', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 63, 64, 65, '[]', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.8351866004095!2d100.56801031420814!3d13.728426201534939!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30e29f01415caee5%3A0x6eeb182d8bb6acf8!2sAmazing+Bangkok+Cyclist!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1505889476616\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', NULL, 'ABC Morning Tour(Amazing Bangkok Cyclist) offers you with the opportunity to see and know the city in depth and at different hours.', NULL, 'Cycle through the heart of Bangkok, taste fresh foods, cross the Chao Phraya river on a long tail boat. Bangkok will open all its secrets & gems to you!', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(9, 27, 'TH', 32, 'ABC Afternoon Tour', 'abc-afternoon-tour', '<p>ABC afternoon tour will give you an insight in the lifes of the local people, walk over an old squeaky wooden bridge and explore communities build under the highway and next to the railway. This part of the tour will give you a very good impression about the daily rituals of the local people. After a drink stop we will cycle to the pier where we will cross the Chao Praya river with our longtail boat. Your bicycles will be carried out of the longtail boat for you. We arrived in the green heart of Bangkok.</p>', '#98094F', '<p><strong>Tour&nbsp;Duration:</strong>&nbsp;13.00-17.00<br />\r\n<strong>Distance:</strong>&nbsp;Approximately 13-16 km</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Meeting point</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ABC Office&nbsp;:&nbsp;10/ 5-7, Soi Ari, Sukhumvit Road Soi 26, Klongton, Klong Toey, Bangkok 10110, Thailand</p>', 10, 1, 0, 1, 'THB', 26000, 0, 104000, 0, 0, 0, '2016-10-27 13:37:34', 1609350, '[\"Coffee or tea upon arrival\",\"Free use of the internet\",\"Free photo\\u2019s of the day\",\"Comfortable and well maintained mountain or city bikes\",\"Water , fruit, snacks , soft drink\",\"Guide fee\",\"Boat transfers\",\"Refreshing towel upon return\"]', '[\"Pick up and drop off from your hotel\",\"Any extra drinks\\/food not provided by your guide\",\"Any alcoholic drinks are prohibited during the tours\",\"Transportation costs if the customer wish to return to before the end of the tour\"]', 130000, '- Cancellation less than 72 hours to prior to the activity, there will be 100% charge\r\n- Any kind of amendment must be done 48 hours to prior to the activity.\r\n- No show will be charged 100%.', 29, NULL, '2017-10-30 09:06:51', NULL, 'ChIJ82ENKDJgHTERIEjiXbIAAQE', 1, 'ABC Office : 10/ 5-7, Soi Ari, Sukhumvit Road Soi 26, Klongton, Klong Toey, Bangkok 10110, Thailand', '+6626656364', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Asia/Bangkok', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 63, 64, 65, '[]', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1