(10, 27, 'TH', 33, 'ABC Day Tour', 'abc-day-tour', '<p>ABC Biking day tour will give you a unique insight into the lifestyles of the local people in Bangkok. We will guide you through all layers of society, from high sky scrapers through Bangkok&rsquo;s biggest fresh market which is a jaw dropping experience. Here you will see vegetables you&rsquo;ve never seen before while lively chickens and fishes are jumping around. After a small tropical fruit break we will cycle through the small communities built up under the highway, where we will end up at the pier.</p>', '#603607', '<p><strong>Tour&nbsp;Duration:</strong>&nbsp;10.00-15.00 (Monday to Friday)<br />\r\n<strong>Distance:</strong>&nbsp;Approximately 16-20&nbsp;km</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Meeting point</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ABC Office&nbsp;:&nbsp;10/ 5-7, Soi Ari, Sukhumvit Road Soi 26, Klongton, Klong Toey, Bangkok 10110, Thailand</p>', 10, 1, 0, 1, 'THB', 36000, 0, 144000, 0, 0, 0, '2016-10-27 14:23:53', 1609350, '[\"Coffee or tea upon arrival\",\"Free use of the internet\",\"Free photo\\u2019s of the day\",\"Comfortable and well maintained mountain or city bikes\",\"Water , fruit, snacks , soft drink\",\"Guide fee\",\"Boat transfers\",\"Refreshing towel upon return\"]', '[\"Pick up and drop off from your hotel\",\"Any extra drinks\\/food not provided by your guide\",\"Any alcoholic drinks are prohibited during the tours\",\"Transportation costs if the customer wish to return to before the end of the tour\"]', 180000, '- Cancellation less than 72 hours to prior to the activity, there will be 100% charge\r\n- Any kind of amendment must be done 48 hours to prior to the activity.\r\n- No show will be charged 100%.', 29, NULL, '2017-10-30 09:04:21', NULL, 'ChIJ82ENKDJgHTERIEjiXbIAAQE', 1, 'ABC Office : 10/ 5-7, Soi Ari, Sukhumvit Road Soi 26, Klongton, Klong Toey, Bangkok 10110, Thailand', '+6626656364', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Asia/Bangkok', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 63, 64, 65, '[]', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/emb